title: Chevy Chase - Classic Movises1978-1997 (20 Movies + Eng sub)
description:
This pack includes 20 of Chevy Chase most classic and memorable movies from 1978-1997...

All of these movies are DvDrip and contains Cover art for every film...

The pack Includes English subs for 8 movies, I have only checked if they sync, I have not done a full check of the subs accuracy...
